# Project Scope

## Core Goal

Build an AI-powered assistant that can answer market intelligence questions using UK business data.

## Phase 1
- project blueprint
- repository structure
- dataset selection
- core business questions

## Phase 2
- data cleaning
- exploratory analysis
- insight design
- chart generation

## Phase 3
- Streamlit interface
- filters and summaries
- user question handling

## Phase 4
- AI integration
- prompt design
- answer generation
- decision-support suggestions

## Phase 5
- GitHub documentation
- screenshots
- Medium article
- LinkedIn publication

## Success Criteria

The final system should:
- answer natural-language questions
- show supporting charts and insights
- use real UK business data
- demonstrate clear business relevance
- function as a portfolio-grade flagship project
